title: Golden Globes
body: Taylor made a surprise appearance at the Golden Globe Awards. She looked so confident presenting the award for Best Original Song and it made me realise how far she has come over the past few years. She persevered through such a hateful period but remained the same kind and generous person she has always been. It makes me so happy to know she is enjoying her success again.
